<item>
            <title>[SPR-2943] Unable to set Integer parameter for Jasperreports in views.properties</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2943</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve just experienced the same problem as Matt Raible in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-1198&quot; title=&quot;Cannot define exporter parameters for JasperReports view when using properties configuration&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-1198&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-1198&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: I get a ClassCastException (String) for this view properties configuration:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;simpleReport.exporterParameters&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;net.sf.jasperreports.engine.export.JRPdfExporterParameter.PERMISSIONS&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;=2052&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using Jasperrepors 1.2.7. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="15690">SPR-2943</key>
            <summary>Unable to set Integer parameter for Jasperreports in views.properties</summary>
